    <section id="content"> 
     <h2>RIT Residence Halls Association</h2> 
     <p>Hello and welcome to the Residence Hall Association, commonly known as RHA. We are located in the tunnels between Grace Watson and Gleason Hall. Stop by during office hours to rent DVDs, hang out and eat candy, grab some popcorn, or see us for our monthly BBQs.</p> 
     <h2>Hockey Season!</h2> 
     <p>Drop by RHA for free hockey tickets when you bring us a can of soup. For each can of soup (maximum of two per game) we'll give you one ticket. Please don't skimp and bring a tiny can of soup, these cans of soup are donated to Foodlink. Check the poster on the office door for which game's tickets we have.</p> 
     <h2>Upcoming Events</h2> 
     <h3>RHA BBQ! <span>Sunday, March 15th · 4:00 – 6:00pm</span></h3> 
     <p>Join us at the sundial for a yummy BBQ, and free food! Grab yourself a free hot dog, hamburger, veggie or vegan burger from the lovely RHA staff. Food is limited so come early when you see the smoke rising!</p> 
     <h3>RHA BBQ! <span>Wednesday, April 15th · 4:00 – 6:00pm</span></h3> 
     <p>Join us at the sundial for a yummy BBQ, and free food! Grab yourself a free hot dog, hamburger, veggie or vegan burger from the lovely RHA staff. Food is limited so come early when you see the smoke rising!</p> 
     <h3>RHA BBQ! <span>Friday, May 15th · 4:00 – 6:00pm</span></h3> 
     <p>Join us at the sundial for a yummy BBQ, and free food! As the last BBQ of the semester come and make your own SMOREs and take a break from studying for finals!</p> 
    </section> 
    <section id="sidebar"> 
     <h3>Free Monthly BBQ</h3> 
     <p>Join us the 15th of every month for a BBQ completely on us. Stop by to grab a hotdog, hamburger, or a veggie burger!</p> 
